{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-feature-js","path":"/learning","webpackCompilationHash":"43a07f76784e304bf1a0","result":{"data":{"feature":{"frontmatter":{"columns":2,"bgColor":"52579F","SEOText":"As new web technologies emerge and evolve, it can be challenging to keep your skills fresh and knowledge up to date. CodeSandbox helps you take a hands-on approach to learn new libraries and frameworks by making it easy to try things out and understand how things really work.","description":"Take a hands-on approach to learning new tech.","tweetText":"CodeSandbox is my life now.","tweetJob":"Software Engineer Educator","ctaText":null,"ctaLink":null,"tweetName":"Kent C. Dodds","tweetHandle":"kentcdodds","coverReversed":true,"coverSmaller":true,"coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/learning-31da189d534de2cdb5d3c7720b59de3c.svg"}},"fields":{"title":"Learning"},"html":"<div>\n<h3 id=\"quickly-try-out-frameworks-and-libraries\"><a href=\"#quickly-try-out-frameworks-and-libraries\" aria-label=\"quickly try out frameworks and libraries permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quickly try out frameworks and libraries</h3>\n<p>Start from a ready-made template for any popular framework, including React,\nVue, Angular, or others. There’s no setup or boilerplate code to write—go\nstraight to experimenting with code and concepts.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3 id=\"code-anywhere-on-any-device\"><a href=\"#code-anywhere-on-any-device\" aria-label=\"code anywhere on any device permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code anywhere, on any device</h3>\n<p>You can use CodeSandbox on any device with a web browser. Take your code with\nyou and work learning into your life—whether that’s coding on the go, at school,\nat work, or from home.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3 id=\"re-use-code-shared-by-the-community\"><a href=\"#re-use-code-shared-by-the-community\" aria-label=\"re use code shared by the community permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Re-use code shared by the community</h3>\n<p>Leverage the collective knowledge of the CodeSandbox community. Search more than\n3M forkable sandboxes to see how others have tackled a problem or used a feature\nto kickstart your understanding.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3 id=\"learn-faster-together\"><a href=\"#learn-faster-together\" aria-label=\"learn faster together permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Learn faster together</h3>\n<p>With Live, you can work on code with friends or colleagues in real-time, just\nlike in a Google Doc.</p>\n<p>Pair up and share knowledge by walking through code. Or send a sandbox link to\nsomeone to get help or provide a solution.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3 id=\"fork-official-sandboxes-for-open-source-projects\"><a href=\"#fork-official-sandboxes-for-open-source-projects\" aria-label=\"fork official sandboxes for open source projects permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fork official sandboxes for open source projects</h3>\n<p>Thousands of projects use CodeSandbox to host their code examples, making it\neasy for you to get started with them.</p>\n</div>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"07bb2b0a-f245-54ec-b492-4d72081217a9"}}}